data.title: Privilege locks Faithless, Sasha, David Morales, more for opening party
data.meta_description: Privilege Ibiza has locked in Faithless (DJ set), David Morales, Danny Avila and more artists for its 2018 opening party, which is scheduled for Friday, 25th May.  The opening party also welcomes Darius Syrossian, Nick Curly + Joshua, a live performance from Guti, a special b2b sunrise set from Sasha and Kölsch and others.
data.text:
Privilege Ibiza has locked in Faithless (DJ set), David Morales, Danny Avila and more artists for its 2018 opening party, which is scheduled for Friday, 25th May.

The opening party also welcomes Darius Syrossian, Nick Curly + Joshua, a live performance from Guti, a special b2b sunrise set from Sasha and Kölsch and others.

The opening party kicks off a busy season for Privilege Ibiza, which once again hosts the Resistance Ibiza residency this summer featuring Carl Cox, Richie Hawtin, Adam Beyer, Maceo Plex and more. Ranked in the top 50 in DJ Mag’s Top 100 Clubs 2018 poll, Privilege Ibiza, the biggest club in the world according to the Guinness Book of Records, celebrates its 25th season this year.

View the Privilege Ibiza 2018 opening party line-up below. For more information on and tickets to the event, visit the official website.
